Enum KeyCode

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<KeyCode>
arc.input.KeyCode
All Implemented Interfaces:
KeyBinds.KeybindValue, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<KeyCode>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum KeyCode
extends java.lang.Enum<KeyCode>
implements KeyBinds.KeybindValue
Enum for storing input codes of mouse, keyboard and controllers.
